Citation.sTitle: Liquid-Liquid Equilibria for the Acetic Acid + Water + Amyl Acetate and Acetic Acid + Water + 2-Methyl Ethyl Acetate Ternary Systems
Citation.sAbstract: Liquid-liquid equilibria for the acetic acid + water + amyl acetate and acetic acid + water + 2-methyl ethyl acetate ternary systems were measured at (304.15, 332.15, and 366.15) K under atmospheric pressure. The experimental data were correlated with the NRTL model, and its interaction parameters were obtained.
